---
title: Sheet Pan Walnut-Crusted Chicken with Honey Dijon Sauce, Cheesy Ciabatta & Roasted Broccoli
description: Weeknights feeling busier and more jam-packed than ever? We hear you! That’s why we’re bringing you a quick and easy meal that’s sure to satisfy your whole pack. This week, we’re featuring chicken coated with a crunchy walnut and panko crust, roasted broccoli, toasted cheesy ciabatta, and a savory-sweet honey Dijon dressing for dipping. This is one 30-minute meal you’ll go nuts over.
